      "answerIndex": 1,
      "explanation": "A \\(30\\text{–}60\\text{–}90\\) triangle has side ratios \\(1 : \\sqrt{3} : 2\\). The side opposite \\(30^\\circ\\) is half the hypotenuse: \\(5\\)."
